ActSelf-Government Treaty Recognizing the Whitecap Dakota Nation / Wapaha Ska Dakota Oyate Act
SubjectOrder Fixing September 1, 2023 as the Day the Self-Government Treaty Recognizing the Whitecap Dakota Nation / Wapaha Ska Dakota Oyate Act Comes into Force
PrecisOrder fixing September 1, 2023 as the day the SELF-GOVERNMENT TREATY RECOGNIZING THE WHITECAP DAKOTA NATION / WAPAHA SKA DAKOTA OYATE ACT COMES INTO FORCE in order to (1) give effect to the Governance Treaty between Whitecap Dakota First Nation and His Majesty in right of Canada; and (2) establish the Whitecap Dakota Nation as a self-governing entity, with jurisdiction and authority over a broad range of matters related to the community’s governance and administration, reserve lands, membership, and programs and services.
RegistrationRegistration: SI/ 2023-0055 Publication Date: 2023-08-16
